videos.description: Texas Tech defensive back Douglas Coleman rips the ball out of D'Onta Foreman's hands just as he about to cross the goal line, and races from one end of the field to the other for an 100-yard touchdown return.
videos.headline: Texas Tech strips Foreman at goal line, returns ball 100 yards for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas Tech strips Foreman at goal line, returns ball 100 yards for TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.description: Texas running back D'Onta Foreman busts through Texas Tech's defensive line and into the backfield, racing into the end zone for a 74-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Foreman breaks free for 74-yard TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Foreman breaks free for 74-yard TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.description: Texas CB Kris Boyd picks off Texas Tech QB Patrick Mahomes II in the end zone to secure the victory for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Texas CB Boyd makes game-winning INT in end zone

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas CB Boyd makes game-winning INT in end zone) 2016/11/05 ESHEET
